msgstr ""
"Der Provider 'groq' erfordert einen API-Schlüssel\n"
"\n"
"Option 1: API-Schlüssel speichern:\n"
"  lokit auth login --provider groq\n"
"\n"
"Option 2: Schlüssel direkt übergeben:\n"
